{
  "texts": [
    "The compounds were incubated on the cells for either 16 h or 24 h. At the specified time point, the medium was carefully removed from the vessel, leaving only 2 μl in the wells.",
    "Celltiter-glo (CTG) reagent (G7572, Promega) was prepared according to the manufacturer's instructions.",
    "Plates with cells were equilibrated at room temperature for 30 min.",
    "Subsequently, 25 μl of CTG reagent was added to the cells.",
    "The plates were then shaken for 2 min and incubated for an additional 15 min at room temperature."
  ]
}